data.name: grdGwaCount.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.GWA, B.GWA_NAME, COUNT(*), B.GWA_COLOR FROM BAS0260 B , VW_OCS_INP1001_01 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.HO_DONG1 = :f_ho_dong AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.GWA = A.GWA GROUP BY A.GWA, B.GWA_NAME, B.GWA_COLOR ORDER BY A.GWA

data.name: layHosilList.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.HO_CODE ,DECODE(NVL(A.HO_SPECIAL_YN,'N'),'N','1','2') HO_STATUS /*총베드수보다 사용베드수가 크면 사용베드수로 베드카운트처리 EX) 1인실인데도 부부로 같이 입원하는 경우 발생 */ ,CASE WHEN NVL(HO_TOTAL_BED,0) >= NVL(HO_USED_BED,0) THEN NVL(HO_TOTAL_BED,0) ELSE NVL(HO_USED_BED,0) END AS HO_BED_COUNT ,A.HO_SEX ,A.HO_CODE_NAME ,A.DOUBLE_HO_YN ,A.HO_SORT FROM BAS0250 A /*-- 병실정보*/ WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.HO_DONG = :f_ho_dong AND TRUNC(SYSDATE) BETWEEN A.START_DATE AND A.END_DATE ORDER BY A.HO_SORT

data.name: layBedList.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.HO_DONG, A.HO_CODE, TO_NUMBER(A.BED_NO) BED_NO, B.TEAM FROM BAS0250 B, BAS0253 A /*-- 병실정보*/ WHERE B.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND B.HO_DONG = :f_ho_dong AND A.HOSP_CODE = B.HOSP_CODE AND A.HO_DONG = B.HO_DONG AND A.HO_CODE = B.HO_CODE AND TRUNC(SYSDATE) BETWEEN B.START_DATE AND B.END_DATE AND TRUNC(SYSDATE) BETWEEN A.FROM_BED_DATE AND NVL(A.TO_BED_DATE,TO_DATE('9998/12/31','YYYY/MM/DD')) -- AND A.BED_STATUS != '05' ORDER BY B.HO_SORT,B.HO_CODE,TO_NUMBER(A.BED_NO,'00')

data.name: layConfirmData.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.FKINP1001 , A.BUNHO , TO_CHAR(A.START_DATE,'YYYY/MM/DD') ORDER_DATE , A.TRANS_TIME , A.TO_GWA , A.TO_DOCTOR , A.TO_RESIDENT , A.TO_HO_CODE1 , A.TO_HO_DONG1 , A.TO_HO_CODE2 , A.TO_HO_DONG2 , A.TRANS_GUBUN , A.TO_BED_NO , A.TO_BED_NO2 , A.FROM_HO_CODE1 , A.FROM_HO_DONG1 , A.FROM_BED_NO , A.TO_HO_GRADE1 , A.TO_HO_GRADE2 , A.TO_KAIKEI_HODONG , A.TO_KAIKEI_HOCODE FROM INP2004 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.FKINP1001 = :f_fkinp1001 AND A.TRANS_CNT = :f_trans_cnt

data.name: layChekNonConfirmOrder.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT 'Y' FROM SYS.DUAL WHERE EXISTS ( SELECT NULL FROM OCS2003 C , VW_OCS_INP1001_RES A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.HO_DONG1 = :f_ho_dong AND A.GA_TOIWON_DATE IS NULL AND A.TOIWON_DATE IS NULL AND C.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND C.BUNHO = A.BUNHO AND C.FKINP1001 = A.PKINP1001 --AND C.ORDER_DATE BETWEEN TRUNC(SYSDATE) AND TRUNC(SYSDATE) + 1 AND NVL(C.RESER_DATE, NVL(C.HOPE_DATE, C.ORDER_DATE)) BETWEEN TRUNC(SYSDATE) AND TRUNC(SYSDATE) + 6 AND C.INPUT_GUBUN LIKE 'D%' --AND SUBSTR(C.ORDER_GUBUN, 2, 1) IN ('B', 'C', 'D') AND C.INPUT_GUBUN != 'D6' AND C.PRN_YN != 'Y' AND NVL(C.TEL_YN, 'N') = 'N' AND (( NVL(C.NDAY_YN, 'N') = 'N' AND C.NURSE_PICKUP_DATE IS NULL AND NVL(C.DC_GUBUN,'N') = 'N' AND NVL(C.DC_GUBUN,'N') = 'N' ) OR (C.NURSE_CONFIRM_DATE IS NOT NULL AND NVL(C.DC_GUBUN,'N') = 'Y' AND NVL(C.DC_YN,'N') = 'N' AND C.NALSU > 0)) AND C.ACTING_DATE IS NULL AND C.JUNDAL_TABLE != 'HOM' UNION SELECT NULL FROM OCS2003 C , VW_OCS_INP1001_RES A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.HO_DONG1 = :f_ho_dong AND A.GA_TOIWON_DATE IS NULL AND A.TOIWON_DATE IS NULL AND C.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND C.BUNHO = A.BUNHO AND C.FKINP1001 = A.PKINP1001 AND C.ACTING_DATE BETWEEN TRUNC(SYSDATE)+1 AND TRUNC(SYSDATE) + 6 --I_ORDER_DATE AND C.IO_GUBUN IS NULL AND C.NALSU < 0 AND C.INPUT_GUBUN != 'D7'/*????*/ AND C.NURSE_PICKUP_USER IS NULL UNION SELECT NULL FROM OCS2015 C , VW_OCS_INP1001_RES A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.HO_DONG1 = :f_ho_dong AND A.GA_TOIWON_DATE IS NULL AND A.TOIWON_DATE IS NULL AND C.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND C.BUNHO = A.BUNHO AND C.FKINP1001 = A.PKINP1001 AND C.ORDER_DATE BETWEEN TRUNC(SYSDATE) AND TRUNC(SYSDATE) + 1 AND C.INPUT_GUBUN LIKE 'D%' AND C.INPUT_GUBUN NOT IN ('D0', 'D3', 'D6', 'D7') AND C.ACT_ID IS NULL AND C.ACT_DATE IS NULL )
